Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Non ci credo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Non avevo intenzione di ucciderti...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E... taglia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ottimo, era buona.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ottima recitazione, Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Divertente il set di un telefilm, vero?
