Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.04,0:03:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\fs18\shad0\bord0\blur0.5\pos(389.9,235.4)}Taeko Mamegaki (24)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:57.55,Default - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenga, un asciugamano.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, grazie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senti, che ne dici\N di venire a cena con me, oggi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, grazie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E dai, che male c'è?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuori questione.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taeko il mese prossimo \Nsi sposa con questo qui.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giusto, Shimazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\p1\bord0\shad0\fscx480\fscy420\c&H99820B&\1a&H68&\blur1.5\pos(442.3,262.4)}m -8 -5 l 7 -5 l 7 7 l -8 7 m 17 0 l 17 0 l 17 0 m 17 7 l 17 7 l 17 7 l 17 7 m -12 7 l -12 7 m -12 0 l -12 0 l -12 7 l -8 7 l -8 0 l 17 0 l 17 7 l 7 7 l -8 0
