Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Era...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)\pos(263,44)\b1\fnTimes New Roman\fs28\c&H0405D5&\bord0\shad0\blur4\1a&HFF&}NI{\c&H0405D5&\1a&H00&}MA{\c&H0405D5&\1a&HFF&}I{\c&H0405D5&\1a&H00&}ME
